    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un redsi/ weens Muhris\nbtja ahra pee ta Nannma wiṣṣ-\napkahrt/ un ta Wibra Rohkâ\nbtja weena mehrama Rihkste fe-\nschas Ohlektis Gaxxumâ/ weena\nOhlektis bija ta ka zitta Ohlektâ/\nn (wehl) weenu Planksti gazru.\nUn wiṣṣb mehroja tahs Ehxas\nPlattumu weennu Rihksti/ un to\nAugstumu weenu Rihksti."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiṣσb nahze pee tahm\nWahrtim/ kas bija prett Rihta-\nPuffi/ un wiṣσb uskahpe us\nwinna Pakahvehm/ un mehroja\nto Wahrtu Sleekfni/ weena\nRihkste bija tas Plattums/ un\nto ohtru Sleekfni/ kur tas Plat-\ntums weena Rihkste bija."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un iktatrâ Kambaris bija\nweenu Rihksti Gaxxumâ/ un\nweenu Rihksti Plattuma/ un\nstarp teem Kambareem (mehro-\nja wiṣσb) peezas Ohlektis/ un\nto Wahrtu Sleekfni pee to\nWahrtu Pagalmja no Eeksch-\npuffes weennu Rihksti."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir wiṣσb mehroja to\nWahrtu Pagalmju/ no Eeksch-\npuffes weenu Rihksti."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiṣσb mehroja to\nohtru Wahrtu Pagalmju/ tur\nbtja astonas Ohlektis/ un winna\nMargahm diwi Ohlektis/ un to\nWahrtu Pagalmju no Eeksch-\npuffes."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un to Wahrtu Kambaru\nprett Rihta Puffes bija trihs no\nschitês/ un trihs no ohtras Puf-"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wehl mehroja wiṣσb to\nPlattumu to Wahrtu Durwju\ndefinitis Ohlektis/ to Wahrtu\nGaxxumu trihspadefinitis Oh-\nlektis."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un us to Kambaro Preek-\nschu bija tahda Starpiba wee-\nnas Ohlektis no schihs Puffes/\nun weenas Ohlektis Starpiba no\nwinnas Puffes/ bet iktatrâ\nKambaris bija no feschahm Oh-\nlektim no schihs Puffes/ un fe-\nschas Ohlektis no winnas Puf-\nfes."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad mehroja wiṣσb tahs\nWahrtis no weena Kambara\nJumta/ lihds tam Jumtain ta\n(ohtca Kambara/) tas Plat-\ntums bija diwidesinitis peezas\nOhlektis/ un weenas Durwis\nbija ohtrahm pretti."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiṣσb darrija arridsan\nMargas no teschdefinitis Ohlek-\ntis/ un preektch iktatras Mar-\ngas weenu Pagalmju wiṣσp-\nkahrt tahm Wahrtim."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no to Wahrtu Preek-\nschas/ kur ee-eet lihds ta Pa-\ngalmja Preeksh Gallain/ pee\ntahm eekschejahm Wahrtim/ bi-\nja peezdefinitis Ohlektis."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un pee teem Kambareem\nbija fchauri Lohgi/ un pee winnu\nMargahm us Eekchu pee tahm\nWahrtim wiṣσpakahrt/ ta arri\npee teem Preeksh-Namneem/\nRr"
    }
  ],
